The portal is written in Python3.12. If you had problems with installing Flask or anything by pip try this commands first

Upgrade pip
py -m ensurepip --upgrade

upgrade virtualenv
pip install --upgrade virtualenv

then try to manualy install Flask
pip install Flask

after or before installing Flask upgrade setuptools as well,
 this module was changed form 3.10 up so not upgrating could cause problems with distutils during installatiopns
python -m pip install --upgrade setuptools

After installing python3.12 and content of requirements.txt you should be able to run application on locally with command
flask --app . run
